_sText:
Hi there

Me and a mate (snitchables) decided to create an aim map each, just as a little competition. 

This is my map, its mainly based around de_train. I used the 3d skybox, light_enviroment and the skybox from de_train to give it a train feel.

EDIT: Re-uploaded and changed the lighting so it is equal for both teams.

Hope you enjoy the map. Thanks for looking :D
